				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "In AD, Ikaron is initially dour and judgmental; if the player convinces him to have a drink in his separate dialogue, he opens up a bit. Rhy maintains his upbeat spirit the whole time.\nIkaron and Rhy are conversing during a party thrown in the player's camp. The player has just defeated the goblins that threatened to kill the Tieflings."
				}
